      "description": "Offering a driver-focused 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six with individual throttle bodies. This example boasts a crisp 6-speed Getrag manual transmission and a factory-spec limited-slip differential. The Double VANOS system has been recently serviced, and the rear subframe has been proactively reinforced\u2014a critical preventative measure for this chassis. Suspension remains taut with refreshed bushings and Bilstein dampers. While showing minor patina consistent with its age, the mechanical integrity is excellent, providing linear power delivery up to its 8,000 RPM redline. A turn-key performance machine for the discerning pilot.",
